<br>
Mage DS (better then druid)<br>
Bard DS<br>
DS potion<br>
Arms off ragefire after he goes dragon<br>
Ring of the 8th<br>
<br>
I know there is one or 2 that I'm missing, but once you crack about 90 you start to get into stacking issues. Fiery might off the BP for example won't stack with the ring of the 8th. Check out safehouse. I'm sure they have a list there somewhere of the maximum non-exploit DS you can have.<br>
<br>
Oh, one more thing. People who have GM quest items that give DSs stack with all those things I listed. There is someone on my server who can self buff himself to 118 DS. That's no mage, no bard, though he is a Druid. <p>Shelrabbi Hassida<BR>
